The '''Karlatt system''' was a [[Star system/Legends|star system]] in the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Galactic Core]], a quarter hour via [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] from [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It contained three inhabited [[Planet/Legends|planets]]: [[Karlatt]], [[Yasla]], and [[Ymura]].

A notable space battle happened in the system. The [[Artificial intelligence/Legends|AI's]] [[Droid/Legends|droid]]-manned fleet, gathered around the [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of the planet [[Karlatt]], engaged both [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] and [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] armadas. When the droids were freed from their [[Slavery/Legends|slavery]] by the destruction of the AI, the droid fleet abandoned the system. The Imperials later falsely blamed the droid revolt on the Rebel Alliance.

